summary: An Ordinance relating to, and providing for, the payment of the cost and expense of the condemnation of a public alley twenty (20) feet in width over and across a portion of Section Nineteen (19), Township Twenty-four (24) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M., from East Marginal Way to Commerical Waterway No. 1, as provided in Ordinance No. 43273, and repealing Ordinance No. 46657.
